</p></section><section id="GUID-CAB53886-53D4-4E0F-B6E4-F23235AF7530" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Start the test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the roll to use. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Double check and confirm the media thickness. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The Printhead Uniformity Test chart is now printed. 
